SECTION_CONTENT:
13.1. Waste treatment methods
Waste from Residues/Unused Products
Should not be released into the environment. Disposal should be in accordance with applicable regional, national and local
laws and regulations.
Contaminated Packaging
Dispose of in accordance with local regulations.
Other Information
Do not flush to sewer. Do not empty into drains. Do not let this chemical enter the environment.
